      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-cared-for ride? This vehicle is in good condition and has been a dependable performer, ready to take you on many more miles! It's been well-maintained and drives great, though you'll find some minor, honest signs of use that come with a pre-owned car. It\u2019s a fantastic choice for anyone seeking quality and value!",
